343	// Delta selection runs synchronously up front via
344	// packfile.DeltaSelector. The selected objects are then handed back to
345	// a packfile.Encoder behind a passthrough ObjectSelector, so the
346	// encoder's write phase (Encode → encode(objects)) streams pack bytes
347	// continuously into an io.Pipe to the HTTP request body. This avoids
348	// the mid-stream stall that occurs when Encode runs selection itself —
349	// CDN edges treat the resulting idle gap as a stalled upload and close
